self as I clicked through the slides on the top, and followed along on the bottom as if I were a participant myself.","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"IFf35gFYVF"}],"key":"CjwZgld3na"}],"key":"GA8M4tGOyz"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I split the recording into roughly ","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"key":"LhFLmGZHrh"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5 minute sections","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"key":"dKqCUJEUhL"}],"key":"PO27BSYLRW"},{"type":"text","value":".\nI’d stop the recording briefly for each section, take a quick breather, and then move on to recording the next. This ensured that I had a moment to collect myself and if I messed up a section, I’d only have to re-record 5 minutes instead of 30.","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"key":"dG64JcSxlu"}],"key":"NDWMLzzQtN"}],"key":"yvyNmJjnya"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"After the recording, I stitched together each of the sections and did a simple fade-out / fade-in using the built-in ","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"key":"borzQapudJ"},{"type":"link","url":"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/create-films-with-video-editor-94e651f8-a5be-ae03-3c50-e49f013d47f6","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"